{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1000,"text":"I dedicated the past two years\nto understanding"},{"time":3233,"text":"how people achieve their dreams."},{"time":5598,"text":"When we think about the dreams we have,"},{"time":7599,"text":"and the dent we want to leave\nin the universe,"},{"time":10132,"text":"it is striking to see how big\nof an overlap there is"},{"time":13677,"text":"between the dreams that we have,\nand projects that never happen."}]},{"cues":[{"time":17323,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":18515,"text":"So I'm here to talk to you today"},{"time":20321,"text":"about five ways\nhow not to follow your dreams."}]},{"cues":[{"time":25223,"text":"One: Believe in overnight success."},{"time":29549,"text":"You know the story, right?"},{"time":31285,"text":"The tech guy built a mobile app\nand sold it very fast for a lot of money."},{"time":36765,"text":"You know, the story may seem real,\nbut I bet it's incomplete."},{"time":40648,"text":"If you go investigate further,"},{"time":42725,"text":"the guy has done 30 apps before"},{"time":44845,"text":"and he has done a master's\non the topic, a PhD."},{"time":47719,"text":"He has been working\non the topic for 20 years."}]},{"cues":[{"time":51822,"text":"This is really interesting."},{"time":53167,"text":"I myself have a story in Brazil\nthat people think is an overnight success."},{"time":58796,"text":"I come from a humble family,"},{"time":61052,"text":"and two weeks before\nthe deadline to apply for MIT,"},{"time":64547,"text":"I started the application process."},{"time":66819,"text":"And, voil√†! I got in."},{"time":69732,"text":"People may think\nit's an overnight success,"},{"time":72559,"text":"but that only worked\nbecause for the 17 years prior to that,"},{"time":76905,"text":"I took life and education seriously."},{"time":79150,"text":"Your overnight success story\nis always a result"},{"time":82617,"text":"of everything you've done\nin your life through that moment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":86712,"text":"Two: Believe someone else\nhas the answers for you."},{"time":90465,"text":"Constantly, people want\nto help out, right?"},{"time":92819,"text":"All sorts of people: your family,\nyour friends, your business partners,"},{"time":96188,"text":"they all have opinions\non which path you should take:"},{"time":99431,"text":"\"And let me tell you,\ngo through this pipe.\""},{"time":101697,"text":"But whenever you go inside,"},{"time":103491,"text":"there are other ways\nyou have to pick as well."},{"time":106244,"text":"And you need to make\nthose decisions yourself."},{"time":109420,"text":"No one else has the perfect\nanswers for your life."},{"time":113301,"text":"And you need to keep picking\nthose decisions, right?"},{"time":115882,"text":"The pipes are infinite\nand you're going to bump your head,"},{"time":118687,"text":"and it's a part of the process."}]},{"cues":[{"time":121806,"text":"Three, and it's very subtle\nbut very important:"},{"time":126004,"text":"Decide to settle\nwhen growth is guaranteed."},{"time":128705,"text":"So when your life is going great,"},{"time":130756,"text":"you have put together a great team,"},{"time":133091,"text":"and you have growing revenue,\nand everything is set --"},{"time":136477,"text":"time to settle."},{"time":138478,"text":"When I launched my first book,"},{"time":140023,"text":"I worked really, really hard\nto distribute it everywhere in Brazil."},{"time":143196,"text":"With that, over three million\npeople downloaded it,"},{"time":145616,"text":"over 50,000 people bought physical copies."},{"time":148332,"text":"When I wrote a sequel,\nsome impact was guaranteed."},{"time":152600,"text":"Even if I did little, sales would be OK."},{"time":156204,"text":"But OK is never OK."},{"time":158138,"text":"When you're growing towards a peak,"},{"time":160448,"text":"you need to work harder than ever\nand find yourself another peak."},{"time":164546,"text":"Maybe if I did little,"},{"time":166262,"text":"a couple hundred thousand\npeople would read it,"},{"time":168486,"text":"and that's great already."},{"time":170435,"text":"But if I work harder than ever,"},{"time":172255,"text":"I can bring this number up to millions."},{"time":175383,"text":"That's why I decided, with my new book,\nto go to every single state of Brazil."},{"time":179120,"text":"And I can already see a higher peak."},{"time":181049,"text":"There's no time to settle down."}]},{"cues":[{"time":183238,"text":"Fourth tip, and that's really important:"},{"time":186481,"text":"Believe the fault is someone else's."},{"time":189961,"text":"I constantly see people saying,"},{"time":192157,"text":"\"Yes, I had this great idea,\nbut no investor had the vision to invest.\""},{"time":196146,"text":"\"Oh, I created this great product,"},{"time":197924,"text":"but the market is so bad,\nthe sales didn't go well.\""},{"time":201834,"text":"Or, \"I can't find good talent;\nmy team is so below expectations.\""},{"time":206683,"text":"If you have dreams,"},{"time":208216,"text":"it's your responsibility\nto make them happen."},{"time":211663,"text":"Yes, it may be hard to find talent."},{"time":214220,"text":"Yes, the market may be bad."},{"time":216321,"text":"But if no one invested in your idea,"},{"time":218475,"text":"if no one bought your product,"},{"time":220368,"text":"for sure, there is something there\nthat is your fault."}]},{"cues":[{"time":223380,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":225405,"text":"Definitely."},{"time":227052,"text":"You need to get your dreams\nand make them happen."},{"time":229950,"text":"And no one achieved their goals alone."},{"time":233162,"text":"But if you didn't make them happen,\nit's your fault and no one else's."},{"time":237310,"text":"Be responsible for your dreams."}]},{"cues":[{"time":241019,"text":"And one last tip, and this one\nis really important as well:"},{"time":246046,"text":"Believe that the only things that matter\nare the dreams themselves."},{"time":250892,"text":"Once I saw an ad,\nand it was a lot of friends,"},{"time":254126,"text":"they were going up a mountain,\nit was a very high mountain,"},{"time":257118,"text":"and it was a lot of work."},{"time":258384,"text":"You could see that they were sweating\nand this was tough."},{"time":261402,"text":"And they were going up,\nand they finally made it to the peak."},{"time":264778,"text":"Of course, they decided\nto celebrate, right?"},{"time":266869,"text":"I'm going to celebrate, so,\n\"Yes! We made it, we're at the top!\""},{"time":270874,"text":"Two seconds later,\none looks at the other and says,"},{"time":273508,"text":"\"OK, let's go down.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":275446,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":276730,"text":"Life is never about the goals themselves."},{"time":279468,"text":"Life is about the journey."},{"time":281940,"text":"Yes, you should enjoy\nthe goals themselves,"},{"time":284301,"text":"but people think that you have dreams,"},{"time":287146,"text":"and whenever you get to reaching\none of those dreams,"},{"time":289785,"text":"it's a magical place\nwhere happiness will be all around."},{"time":293851,"text":"But achieving a dream\nis a momentary sensation,"},{"time":297272,"text":"and your life is not."},{"time":299211,"text":"The only way to really achieve\nall of your dreams"},{"time":302521,"text":"is to fully enjoy every step\nof your journey."},{"time":306451,"text":"That's the best way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":307638,"text":"And your journey is simple --\nit's made of steps."},{"time":310038,"text":"Some steps will be right on."},{"time":311992,"text":"Sometimes you will trip."},{"time":314228,"text":"If it's right on, celebrate, because\nsome people wait a lot to celebrate."},{"time":318849,"text":"And if you tripped,\nturn that into something to learn."},{"time":321996,"text":"If every step becomes something\nto learn or something to celebrate,"},{"time":327446,"text":"you will for sure enjoy the journey."}]},{"cues":[{"time":330071,"text":"So, five tips:"},{"time":331797,"text":"Believe in overnight success,"},{"time":334231,"text":"believe someone else\nhas the answers for you,"},{"time":336657,"text":"believe that when growth is guaranteed,\nyou should settle down,"},{"time":339683,"text":"believe the fault is someone else's,"},{"time":342029,"text":"and believe that only\nthe goals themselves matter."},{"time":345358,"text":"Believe me, you do that,\nand you will destroy your dreams."}]},{"cues":[{"time":348386,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":349617,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":350814,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":352695,"text":"Thanks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":353916,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}